name: Test that setting a local variable will override a global variable
scenarioId: tiger-test-lib/TigerGlueTest_firstFile:Test that setting a local variable will override a global variable
methodName: Test that setting a local variable will override a global variable

testSteps.description: Given TGR set local feature variable "tiger.tigerGlue.helloTestFeature1" to "local value feature 1st file"
Given TGR set local variable "tiger.tigerGlue.helloTestLocal" to "local value 1st file"
Then TGR assert variable "tiger.tigerGlue.helloTestLocal" matches "local value 1st file"
Then TGR assert variable "tiger.tigerGlue.helloTestFeature1" matches "local value feature 1st file"
Then TGR assert variable "tiger.tigerGlue.helloTestFeature2" matches "global value for helloTestFeature2"

title: Test that setting a local variable will override a global variable
